            "last_activity_date": 1450688413,
            "creation_date": 1450688413,
            "body": "<p>If you already able to read the data in a String then you should use regular expressions to separate the data (one way)<\/p>\n\n<p>You can find a basic tutorial for regular expressions here : <a href=\"http://tutors4all.net/index.php/2015/05/18/regular-expressions-part-1/\" rel=\"nofollow\">http://tutors4all.net/index.php/2015/05/18/regular-expressions-part-1/<\/a><\/p>\n",
